## Limitations

The research is limited by the availability of online resources and the potential bias in historical accounts. Many primary sources from the 1800s may not be accessible online, and interpretations of historical events can vary. Additionally, the focus on American slavery may overlook the global context and experiences of enslaved individuals in other regions during the same period.